the dow jones average of 30 industrials, up 24.70 on tuesday, slipped back 4.31 to 2,076.76 by 2 p.m. today on wall street
gainers outnumbered losers by about 3 to 2 in the overall tally of new york stock exchange-listed issues, with 880 up, 587 down and 456 unchanged
